r=d7.vA("Crush barbs flat with pliers. Barbless hooks reduce injury by 30-50% and make hook removal effortless \u2014 often the fish can be released without even taking it out of the water. In Canada, barbless hooks are required in many waters.","\u26a0\ufe0f Barbless hook rules vary by province \u2014 check your local fishing regulations",B.VL,"Barbless hooks save lives")
