f=d7.vA("If the fish swallowed the hook, DO NOT pull it out. Cut the line as close to the hook as possible. The hook will rust out or pass naturally. Pulling causes fatal internal injuries.","\ud83d\udea8 NEVER pull a swallowed hook \u2014 cut the line instead",B.Vk,"Gut-hooked (swallowed hook): Cut the line")
e=d7.i7("Barbless hooks often fall out with a simple flick of the pliers or even just tension on the line. Many fish can be released without being removed from the water at all.",B.rp,"Barbless hooks = easy release")
